      <br>• Standard lorry: RM200,000
      <br><strong>Premium:</strong> RM120,000</p>

      <p><strong>ROI:</strong> Cold chain premium recovered in 1-2 years through higher revenue. Remaining 3-4 years generate pure profit.</p>

